{"tid":2049427,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"考評局對司法覆核不作回應　不會評閱已取消歷史科分題","createTime":"2020-06-03T12:33:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-03T16:16:02.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4e87bdac15bffef96409dca9f9cee05f6b293712","tid":2049427,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T12:33:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=393211\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D393211&d=ZttPR3oQiG8LQafLEcup%2BFDApO%2Br9QW7Zx2priNtVuo%3D&h=47faa6e8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D393211&h=1d32b823\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=393211</a><br />\n【Now新聞台】有學生就考評局取消中學文憑試歷史科其中一條試題的決定申請司法覆核。<br />\n<br />\n中學生行動籌備平台成員到高等法院遞交入稟狀，入稟狀申請人是平台成員之一，一名姓盧的應屆文憑試歷史科考生，建議答辯人為考評局。<br />\n<br />\n發言人鄭家朗質疑考評局取消歷史科試題的決定違反程序公義，教育局亦無權就考卷內容作出干預，違反《基本法》第34條及137條有關市民享有學術自由的保障。<br />\n<br />\n被取消的試題是一條必答題，佔8分，問考生是否同意「1900至45年間日本為中國帶來的利多於弊」，約5200名考生受影響。<br />\n<br />\n考評局表示，由於個案已經進入司法程序，不作任何回應，亦不會評閱已取消的歷史科分題，其他題目則會繼續進行閱卷，考評局會盡力確保閱卷工作依時完成。"},{"pid":"d46e53585d26ad059965a3a873bab6ed9adc7487","tid":2049427,"uid":33028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T12:35:49.000Z","msg":"審完都放榜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53ba53420267e8985aad28c963653289742941b6","tid":2049427,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d46e53585d26ad059965a3a873bab6ed9adc7487","tid":2049427,"uid":33028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T12:35:49.000Z","msg":"審完都放榜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T12:39:07.000Z","msg":"唔關事<br />\n係唔可以比港共咁易亂黎"},{"pid":"3450c56b4a6bbe0178ef1927596627cb2326ebde","tid":2049427,"uid":288707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score